{"tid":1930483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【藍絲與狗事件】民政總署：李、劉涉違區議員操守指引　告示或未符《酬津指引》原則","createTime":"2020-03-17T14:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T14:38:29.000Z","uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa668a1c93e7b6c1967f2e1f882eb4d41bd83597","tid":1930483,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"深水埗區議員李文浩、劉家衡早前在辦事處張貼「藍絲與狗不得內進」告示，連日來遭建制派支持者上門抗議及搗亂。民政總署今日表示，二人行為涉嫌違反《區議員及區議會轄下委員會成員操守指引》，已去信強烈勸喻他們盡移除告示，並轉介深水埗區議會主席跟進投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%88%87%E7%8B%97%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%BD%B2-%E6%9D%8E-%E5%8A%89%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%93%8D%E5%AE%88%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%E6%88%96%E6%9C%AA%E7%AC%A6-%E9%85%AC%E6%B4%A5%E6%8C%87%E5%BC%95-%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E6%259D%258E-%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AC%25A6-%25E9%2585%25AC%25E6%25B4%25A5%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=e52a5519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E6%259D%258E-%25E5%258A%2589%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2593%258D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AC%25A